**/coverage*.xml

# User / IDE files
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates
**/.vs
**/.idea
**/*.DotSettings.user

# Never commit secrets — keys live in User Secrets / env vars (see README.md)
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/secrets.json

# Claude Code machine-local settings (keep shared .claude/settings.json if you add one)
**/.claude/settings.local.json

# OS cruft
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# Logs
**/*.log
fly.toml
